<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="what-is-a-beep">What is a BEEP?<a href="https://boosterframework.com/blog/0001-purpose-and-guidelines#what-is-a-beep" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to What is a BEEP?" title="Direct link to What is a BEEP?">​</a></h2>
<p>BEEP stands for Booster Evolution Enhancement Proposal. It is a document that describes a change or addition to Booster.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="statuses-of-a-beep">Statuses of a BEEP<a href="https://boosterframework.com/blog/0001-purpose-and-guidelines#statuses-of-a-beep" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Statuses of a BEEP" title="Direct link to Statuses of a BEEP">​</a></h2>
<p>A BEEP can have one of the following statuses:</p>
<div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-caution admonition_xJq3 alert alert--warning"><div class="admonitionHeading_Gvgb"><span class="admonitionIcon_Rf37"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.893 1.5c-.183-.31-.52-.5-.887-.5s-.703.19-.886.5L.138 13.499a.98.98 0 0 0 0 1.001c.193.31.53.501.886.501h13.964c.367 0 .704-.19.877-.5a1.03 1.03 0 0 0 .01-1.002L8.893 1.5zm.133 11.497H6.987v-2.003h2.039v2.003zm0-3.004H6.987V5.987h2.039v4.006z"></path></svg></span>STATUS - DRAFT</div><div class="admonitionContent_BuS1"><p>This status indicates that the BEEP is still being written and is not ready for review.</p></div></div>
<div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-info admonition_xJq3 alert alert--info"><div class="admonitionHeading_Gvgb"><span class="admonitionIcon_Rf37"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2.3c3.14 0 5.7 2.56 5.7 5.7s-2.56 5.7-5.7 5.7A5.71 5.71 0 0 1 1.3 8c0-3.14 2.56-5.7 5.7-5.7zM7 1C3.14 1 0 4.14 0 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm1 3H6v5h2V4zm0 6H6v2h2v-2z"></path></svg></span>STATUS - IN PROGRESS</div><div class="admonitionContent_BuS1"><p>This status indicates that the BEEP has been accepted but is still being implemented.</p></div></div>
